<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ title }}</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-10">
                <!-- Header -->
                <div class="card mb-4">
                    <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt me-2"></i>{{ title }}</h3>
                        <p class="mb-0">Kanwil Kementerian Agama Sulawesi Barat</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        {% for flash_message in app.flashes('success') %}
                            <div class="alert alert-success">
                                <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>{{ flash_message }}
                            </div>
                        {% endfor %}
                        
                        <p>Selamat datang di aplikasi manajemen cuti. Berikut adalah fitur-fitur yang tersedia:</p>
                        
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class="card text-center">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <i class="fas fa-plus-circle fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
                                        <h5>Pengajuan Cuti</h5>
                                        <p class="text-muted">Ajukan permohonan cuti baru</p>
                                        <a href="{{ path('pengajuan_cuti_new') }}" class="btn btn-primary">
                                            <i class="fas fa-plus me-1"></i>Buat Pengajuan
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class="card text-center">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <i class="fas fa-list fa-3x text-info mb-3"></i>
                                        <h5>Riwayat Cuti</h5>
                                        <p class="text-muted">Lihat riwayat pengajuan cuti</p>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-info">
                                            <i class="fas fa-history me-1"></i>Lihat Riwayat
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <div class="card text-center">
                                    <div class="card-body">
                                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-check fa-3x text-success mb-3"></i>
                                        <h5>Hak Cuti</h5>
                                        <p class="text-muted">Cek sisa hak cuti Anda</p>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">
                                            <i class="fas fa-eye me-1"></i>Lihat Hak Cuti
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Validation Success Info -->
                <div class="alert alert-success">
                    <h5><i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>âœ… Validasi Login Berhasil!</h5>
                    <p>Sistem validasi telah berhasil diimplementasikan dengan fitur:</p>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h6><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-1"></i>Validasi NIP:</h6>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Field wajib diisi (#[Assert\NotBlank])</li>
                                <li>Harus 18 digit angka (#[Assert\Regex("/^\d{18}$/")])</li>
                                <li>Pesan error dalam bahasa Indonesia</li>
                                <li>Real-time validation dengan JavaScript</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <h6><i class="fas fa-key me-1"></i>Validasi Password:</h6>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Field wajib diisi (#[Assert\NotBlank])</li>
                                <li>Minimal 8 karakter (#[Assert\Length(min:8)])</li>
                                <li>Harus ada huruf kecil, besar, dan angka (#[Assert\Regex])</li>
                                <li>Visual feedback saat mengetik</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h6><i class="fas fa-code me-1"></i>Teknologi yang Digunakan:</h6>
                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                        <span class="badge bg-primary">Symfony 7.3</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-secondary">Symfony Validator</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-info">PHP 8+ Attributes</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-success">Symfony Form</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-warning">Bootstrap 5</span>
                        <span class="badge bg-danger">Font Awesome 6</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Actions -->
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-body text-center">
                        <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}" class="btn btn-outline-secondary me-2">
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-1"></i>Kembali ke Login
                        </a>
                        <a href="{{ path('app_logout') }}" class="btn btn-outline-danger">
                            <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt me-1"></i>Logout
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>